  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Beverly Alps Hotel &amp; Spa is on a half board basis.</p>
<p>All meals are served in the hotel's restaurant. Every morning there's breakfast buffet with hot and cold options and in the evenings you'll get a three-course meal with a choice. Once a week the hotel have a gala dinner where to can try some local and regional dishes. </p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
