  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Beverly Alps Hotel &amp; Spa exudes a cosy Alpine charm, located just 400 metres from the Pinzolo - Pra Rodont cable car and even closer to the heart of Pinzolo. With spacious rooms, inviting communal areas, and a relaxing wellness zone, this four-star superior hotel is an excellent choice for skiers and those seeking to unwind after a day on the slopes.</p>
<h2><span>Homely comfort</span></h2>
<p>The hotel’s Alpine-themed décor and warm ambiance create a welcoming retreat. The spacious, well-equipped rooms ensure you can settle in and feel at home right away. After unpacking, relax in the bar with a drink, it’s the perfect spot to mingle with the friendly staff, who are always happy to share their top tips and favourite ski runs.</p>
<p>Start your mornings with an extensive breakfast buffet, offering plenty of options to fuel your day. In the evening, enjoy a delicious three-course meal, with many ingredients sourced locally for an authentic taste of the region.</p>
<h2>Prime location</h2>
<p>The Beverly Alps Hotel &amp; Spa is a dream base for serious skiers. Hop on the free shuttle to the lifts and explore the expansive ski area, all while taking in the breath-taking scenery of the Brenta Dolomites National Park. From the gondola, you can tackle the quiet local slopes or venture further toward Madonna di Campiglio and beyond to rack up the miles.</p>
<p>After a thrilling day, relax with a drink at a mountain hut before deciding whether to take on the challenging black run back to Pinzolo or opt for an easier ride down on the gondola.</p>]]></description>
