  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Twin Rooms</strong> are 20m² and sleep two people and have a shower.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Twin Rooms</strong> are 23m² and can sleep up to three people using a single sofa bed and have a shower. </p>
<p><strong>Alpine Suites</strong> are 50m² and can sleep up to four with double bed in the master bedroom and a double sofa bed in the lounge. Rooms come with two bathrooms, one with a shower and the other a jacuzzi bath. They are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Panoramic Suite </strong>are 60m² and located on the top floor. They can sleep up to four with a double bed in the master bedroom and either a double sofa bed or two single sofa beds in the lounge. They have two bathrooms, one with a shower and the other with a bath. Rooms have a panoramic balcony. They are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Standard Twin Rooms for Single Use</strong> are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>TV </li>
<li>Fridge</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
